This page on SteamDB showcases a curated list of games tagged as 'Interactive Fiction'. Interactive fiction is a genre of narrative storytelling in which the audience interacts with the narrative, often by making choices that determine the direction and outcome of the story. These games on SteamDB offer a unique blend of narrative depth and player agency, allowing you to shape your own stories within immersive virtual worlds. Whether you're new to the genre or a seasoned veteran, this collection provides a diverse range of experiences that are sure to captivate and engage you. Explore these interactive stories and uncover the myriad possibilities that lie within.
